text: Prime Lake Whatcom view lot located in Sudden Valley Gate 1. Building plans have been rendered and are waiting for your personal touches. Opportunity awaits as 6 Sanwick is for sale to offer a double lot. Enjoy access to pristine Lake Whatcom with 5 private beaches, hiking trails, 18 hole golf course, and a marina with 2 boat launches. Embrace the tranquility of lakeside living while being just minutes away from Downtown Bellingham. Owner financing options available. Ask your agent for more details.

Welcome home to your perfect blend of tranquility and modern convenience! Spacious and well maintained 2-bed 1-bath condo featuring a stunning view of Mt. Baker from the back patio. New carpet, fresh paint, and timeless hardwood flooring throughout. Enjoy the convenience of a ground floor unit, covered carport parking with a locking storage area. Complemented by newer appliances and a newer water heater. Pet friendly along with a well-managed HOA, every detail is taken care of, ensuring worry-free living. Perfectly located in the active and assessable community of Ferndale. Enjoy a breathtaking sunrise view and only be minutes to downtown Ferndale that offers a calendar full of fun and inclusive events! This condo is truly a hidden gem!

WELCOME TO BALFOUR VILLAGE PHASE 2! Affordable living, JUST COMPLETED rambler in a brand new community. This cozy home features a large lot with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, 3 car garage, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops & A/C. Come enjoy tranquil living with peace and quiet and natural surroundings. Only 30 minutes to Bellingham! SELLER OFFERING UP TO 2% TOWARDS BUYERS RATE BUY DOWN!

Timeless one-level home in the desirable Geneva neighborhood. This open-concept design is perfect for entertaining, an easy flow from the culinary kitchen with a massive island + dining and the great room with a gas fireplace. Luxury finishes with 10 ft and vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, built-in bookcases + sideboard, wood-wrapped windows and more. Split bedrooms with Primary suite on a wing of its own. Flex room at entry: could be den/office or formal dining. Gorgeous hardscaping with flagstone patios, one-covered for 4-season use + fully-fenced grass yard with hot/cold dog wash station. Situated on 1/4+ acre corner lot offering privacy and mature landscaping. Close to Waldorf School, Lake Whatcom and Euclid Park with public beach.

Experience the perfect blend of comfort and luxury in this stunning 4 bed, 3 bathroom home on a spacious 5.6-acre parcel in Ferndale, WA. This newly renovated property features modern elegance with updated floors, kitchen, and fixtures. Enjoy relaxing evenings by the cozy fireplace or unwind in the hot tub after a long day. With a large shop included, there's plenty of space for all your hobbies and projects. Nestled in a peaceful and secluded lot, yet conveniently located near I-5, this oasis offers tranquility and privacy while still being close to amenities. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to make this dream home yours! Schedule a viewing today.

Peaceful oasis at the entry to Whatcom Falls Park. Relax in privacy on the deck overlooking the pond with waterfall, mature goldfish, lush plantings and surrounding forest. Fully fenced backyard has lawn, blueberries and raspberries. Fenced garden has raised beds and apple trees. Cute artist studio with lots of natural light. Have fun with the Little Free Library. Large garage with work bench and storage shelving. Separate storage shed for yard tools. New features: electrical panel, water heater, and roof. New bathroom flooring, many new light fixtures and fresh paint throughout. Please note new offer review date The home is clean, fresh and very well maintained in an amazing location. Must see to appreciate the absolute tranquility.

Prime Lake Whatcom view lot located in Sudden Valley Gate 1. Opportunity awaits as 4 Sanwick is for sale to offer a double lot. This turn key offering comes with building plans. Sudden Valley offers an array of desirable attributes, including breathtaking natural beauty, a close-knit community, and a range of amenities. Enjoy access to pristine Lake Whatcom with 5 private beaches, hiking trails, 18 hole golf course, and a marina with 2 boat launches. Embrace the tranquility of lakeside living while being just minutes away from Downtown Bellingham. Owner financing options available. Ask agents for more info!

Better than new! This meticulously maintained 3 bed / 2 bath home is move in ready and just waiting for it's new owners. Primary bedroom on main level with office space or book nook space as well. Open concept on upper level featuring views of the Frasier Valley and Canadian mountains. 2 covered decks makes enjoying the PNW outdoors a bit more enjoyable. Fully fenced yard with garden space and chicken coop ready for your own personal backyard mini farm. Beautiful home that will not disappoint even the pickiest buyer.

This is the one you've been waiting for! With over 4800 sq ft & sprawling Mt Baker views, this dream home is nothing short of perfection with every last detail. Encompassed by natural landscape and endless variety of fruit trees, and seasonal foliage for year round blissful colors. The property boasts 3 spacious levels, 4 bds with den/offices that could be adtl bdr. Includes fully separate basement ADU & a separate main floor studio ADU. Freshly painted, all new high end appliances for a chef's kitchen, & an oversized detached shop for all your outdoor toys and gear. Other amazing features include generator, AC, newer roof w/solar panels, & EV super charger. What more could you ask for? Come tour this amazing property while you still can!

Custom built home with attention to detail everywhere you look. Southern exposure for passive heat and wonderful views. Trex decks with log accents. Hot tub, sauna and prewired diesel generator with 14 day supply of fuel. Full security system on all exterior doors with motion detection on both floors. Garage and shop are heated and fully insulated with 5/8 drywall. 40 amp outlet for car charger available. Pool table and TV's stay. Experience this one of a kind gated community offering a 9 hole executive style golf course, marina, pool, clubhouse, pickleball and tennis courts, saltwater parks and beaches, 2 man made lakes and quiet private roads.

Nestled on 3 acres of serene countryside, this charming rambler offers the quintessential hobby farm lifestyle you've been dreaming of with Mt.Baker views! Spacious 2 car garage & RV parking. Located just a stone's throw away from the Canadian border by Abbotsford. Grow berries in the field & enjoy mature fruit trees, garden space & embrace the rural lifestyle with your very own barn, perfect for housing livestock, storing equipment, or unleashing your creative passions. Enjoy spacious 2 car garage & RV parking. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat, a thriving hobby farm, or simply a place to call home, this is where your story unfolds. Welcome to the life you've always imagined.

Waterfront recreation on Lake Whatcom that includes a remodeled house, a rustic 1939 cabin, & detached garage on 3 lots. Enjoy 108 feet of waterfront, dock and boat lift-even a wind surfer and paddle boat! The main house is casual with a kitchen remodeled about 10 years ago with stainless appliances, natural stone and copper sink. Main floor primary bedroom w/ ensuite that includes a washer/dryer. Living room has a wall of windows to take in the South Bay lake views. Walkout basement has living room used as sleeping space plus another separate bedroom. Rustic charm greets you in the 1939 cabin. There is no heat or appliances, but perfect for summer sleepovers. Lots cannot be devided. Ready to enjoy or rent. Parking for 5+ cars.

Explore this brand-new single-level home featuring 3 bedrooms and 1.75 bathrooms. Enjoy a well-designed floor plan with tasteful finishes and vaulted ceilings. The great room is perfect for entertaining, with a spacious dining area extending from the open kitchen. The kitchen boasts ample storage, quartz countertops, a tiled backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. Retreat to the master suite with a walk-in closet and dreamy master bathroom with a tiled shower and double vanity. Outside, a large covered outdoor living area awaits, perfect for entertaining. Completion expected by mid-March

Step into a seamless blend of modern comfort & classic elegance as you enter this single-level gem, located on the rarely available Kelley Ridge Ct. With just one owner since its construction, this home couldn't be in better condition. Plus, with brand new carpets and luxury vinyl plank floors, it's completely move-in ready. Flooded with natural light from the sky lights & vaulted ceilings you will enjoy the spacious living area with a gas fireplace and dining room. Sliding doors to the backyard, showcasing mature landscaping and a newer composite deck with views of Bellingham Bay. Just wait until you see the three-car garage w/ space for your boat, RV, or third vehicle. This home truly checks all the boxes!

Perfect for vacation life or year round recreation, this very private and well maintained 3BR, 2BA home sits on a large flat lot with great garden space, two large decks and extra tall fencing on three sides. Additional features include bamboo floors, metal roof, newer windows, new appliances in the spacious kitchen including stove, dishwasher and washer & dryer and tons of storage throughout. Located near the foot of the Cascade Mountains, enjoy the best the PNW has to offer including abundant hiking trails and waterfalls, skiing at Mount Baker, fishing in the Nooksack river, stargazing at Artist's Point, camping at Silver Lake and more!

PRICE IMPROVEMENT + $5k Seller concession. Discover the PERFECT blend of COMFORT and convenience in this completely remodeled home with new electrical on acreage. Enjoy a one-level layout with 3BR, 1.75BA and bonus room above the garage. Every detail exudes charm and functionality. From the cozy fireplace in the living room to the serene primary bedroom, relaxation is guaranteed. The recently remodeled bathrooms offer luxury. Outside, lush greenery, firepit and outbuildings await, alongside a substantial 1250 square foot shop. Pride of ownership is evident throughout, showcasing meticulous care and attention to detail. Make this haven your own, where every corner resonates with warmth and comfort, located with easy access to amenities.

Perfect mid county location. Upper floor is a primary suite oasis with 3/4 bathroom, large walk in closet, fireplace and nook/office space. Spacious kitchen with lots of cabinets for all your things with a formal dining area. Large living/family area would be great for entertaining. Plus additional room perfect for an office. Shop out back perfect for storage or to work on projects. Enjoy the hot tub in your private back yard with lots of space for a garden. Peaceful setting on a quiet street, with a short walk to Wiser Lake and boat launch.

Convenient single-story living in Lynden! Set on a large lot, this open-concept home features vaulted ceilings, large windows, custom cabinets + built-in shelving throughout, & central AC. Living room with cozy gas fireplace, spacious kitchen with modern tile backsplash + sunny dining area, & a versatile formal dining area/flex space. Head back to a full bathroom, & 3 good-sized bedrooms including the primary suite with coffered ceilings, walk-in closet, dual vanities, full-height shower, & jetted soaker tub. Outside is the private backyard with 16x14 Trex deck, flower beds, automatic sprinkler system, & a fully-insulated/heated detached shop with cable hookup. Attached 2-car garage, covered front porch & near downtown Lynden. Welcome Home!

5, 000 + sq ft lot, with 2009 RV. Steps away from a comfort station and one of the trails to the Nooksack River. Lot is located in the Glen at Maple Falls recreational park. The Glen has many amenities including but not limited to: 2 club houses, 2 pools, hot tub, sauna, trails, playgrounds, on site library and on site laundry facilities.

Unveil the charm of this 1907 lovingly updated South Hill gem, boasting beautiful bay views. Revel in a bedroom, office space & open bathroom/laundry room, alongside an updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances. Step out to the spacious deck to relish captivating sunsets & prime West-facing Puget Sound boating scenes. The convenient location near Boulevard Park, coupled with a short stroll to Fairhaven, offers exceptional walkability. Below, the ADU offers a bedroom, laundry, kitchen, full bath & potential additional bedroom. With its updated foundation, plumbing, electrical & newer roof, this property offers an excellent opportunity for generating additional rental income or for accommodating multigenerational living.

One level living on a beautiful corner lot with nearly 1/3 of acre. This sunny lot is in a quiet location in a neighborhood that has a rural feel, but a central location in the county - within 10-15 minute drive to Bellingham, Ferndale & Lynden. Chic remodel inside with updated kitchen with granite countertops, remodeled bathroom with new bathtub, vanity & stone countertops. New commercial grade LVP flooring throughout most of the home. The large backyard is fully fenced and features two outbuildings, raised garden beds and a covered patio. This is a must-see!

Welcome to your charming bungalow in Cornwall Park! This prime location offers the perfect blend of convenience & comfort centrally located near downtown Bellingham. This beautifully updated home has been thoughtfully enhanced with a host of modern upgrades; including granite countertops, a stylish backsplash, brand-new stainless steel appliances, gas stove, hood vent, refrigerator, new washer/dryer and a sleek kitchen sink/faucet. The open layout seamlessly flows into the cozy living area, creating a warm & inviting space for entertaining. New Pergo flooring and low-maintenance surfaces complements the aesthetic. French doors lead out to a private outdoor space, perfect for enjoying those Pacific Northwest's summer evenings!

Stunning NW contemporary craftsman in a private neighborhood on Lake Samish! 2018 renovation features luxury finishes - oak hardwood floors, heated tile floors in bathrooms, clear fir door & window trim, stained clear cedar ceilings, & huge windows offering expansive views over the lake & Lookout Mountain. Spacious deck adjoins both living room & primary suite; large windows look out over lawn, private dock, & boat lift, & provide beautiful morning sunrises. Putting green & new hot tub; home is wired for generator. Enjoy lawn games & evening campfires, and all that the lake has to offer: water skiing/wakeboarding/paddle boarding, along with hiking nearby. Minutes from WWU & Bellingham amenities. Come enjoy luxury waterfront living!

Imagine the possiblities for this single level home tucked away in a cul-de-sac in Happy Valley. The home as been renovated since 2021 including an all new heart of the home kitchen, fresh paint and LVP flooring, newer roof & fencing, updated wiring for baseboards, new can lights for a soft glow and refurbished attic and crawl space, just to name a few! The location is close to Fairhaven and I-5 and an easy walk to WWU. The extra large living room can accomodate a large gathering or create spaces for activities or relaxation. The tidy yard is very low maintenance so, you can keep it simple or create a beautiful oasis. A gas line has been installed, for more flexibility to change out appliances and systems. Don't wait on this one!

South-facing waterfront cedar cottage located on desirable Edwards Dr with stunning panoramic ocean views. This property offers front-row seats to watch the boats heading out to sea and whale watching. This well-maintained cottage exhibits exceptional unobstructed views of the San Juan Islands and Mt. Baker and features 3 beds, 1 bath, and a detached shed. Enjoy the wood stove on a brisk summer evening or the A/C on a hot summer day. Bright open-concept living area with vaulted ceilings that features an updated kitchen, large windows with panoramic vistas, and sliding doors onto the expansive deck space. Don't miss out on this legacy property rarely offered!

Don't overlook this fantastic opportunity! Nestled on two city lots, this property from the 1922 era is bursting with potential waiting to be realized. Positioned right in the heart of Bellingham's York neighborhood, it boasts proximity to the picturesque Harriet Spanel Park, enhancing its allure. With a generous lot size of approximately 112' x 80' and supposed zoning adjustments on the horizon, savvy investors stand to gain substantially from this prime investment opportunity. Convenient location near shopping & services. Home is sold AS IS.

Here's your opportunity to live a Lake Samish life in the coveted Calmor Cove! This quaint and cozy one bed, one bath home is the perfect vacation getaway or full-time home just a short distance from Lake Samish and only 5min from I-5! It has a tankless water heater and the roof is only 5 years old! There's a green belt behind the home that gives you peace and privacy. The large deck is perfect for relaxing in your private oasis. Enjoy all the amenities of the park including a dock, clubhouse, public restrooms, lawn area and sport court! Park fees cover water, sewer, and garbage!

Welcome to this beautiful 3-bed, 2.5-bath home featuring a main floor primary suite with a large double-sink ensuite. Just upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms sharing a spacious bathroom. Modern amenities include stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, new furnace, and air conditioning. The outdoor area boasts a fully fenced yard and an expansive patio, ideal for gatherings. Conveniently located just a short walk from Birch Bay's waterfront, dining, and entertainment, this inviting home is a rare find that's sure to be snapped up quickly!

RELOCATION forces sale and dont miss this AMAZING new Kitchen, Imagine owning in USA Bordertown, Completely remodeled rambler with no stairs, Giant 1/3 acre 14, 810 sqft flat lot perfect for animals and all your friends, toys, boats, and RV. 3 bed/2 bath Generous 1, 608 sqft with light and bright open floor plan , 600 plus sqft to get lost in this monster attached 2 car garage. New white shaker kitchen cabinets and bathroom vanities, quartz countertops, stainless appliances, and fresh paint inside and out. Excellent location just minutes to I5 and the Canadian border, all the shopping you can handle. The awesome country feel you have been dreaming of, backyard has 2nd access, cherry and plum trees will add to peace and tranquility!

Enjoy unobstructed panoramic views of Bellingham Bay, the surrounding islands & downtown Bellingham from this prime, end-unit condo at Spinnaker Reach located above the Boulevard Park & boardwalk. This flat features additional windows for more natural light & easy access with no steps from the parking spot to the front door. It has been lovingly maintained by a single family since its inception, presenting a unique opportunity for you to personalize this already exceptional space to your taste. It's adjacent to gated access to the city's trail system, you can enjoy easy walks to the park or a scenic route all the way to downtown. Recent upgrades include new siding, decks, windows, & roof. Also features seasonal pool, sauna & clubhouse room.

The light floods through this move-in ready zero lot line single level home in the desirable Homestead Community. Vaulted 9 ft ceilings, radiant heat, hardwood floors, quartz countertops, all stainless steel appliances included, huge master suite, water filtration, covered patio, 10 fruit trees, fully fenced backyard, raised flower beds, 2 sheds and so much more. Don't miss your opportunity to call this home today!

Discover lakeside living in beautiful Sudden Valley! Ideal for every lifestyle, this home features space to relax and entertain. The serene primary suite features a private deck with a view. And living is easy in the great room featuring the kitchen, dining and living areas, with direct access to the deck. The flexible basement layout presents potential for a bonus suite, complete with plumbing for a kitchenette, and a shower for cleaning up after some lake time. Mature landscaping, 2-car detached garage, and more-welcome home!

This well-maintained 1906 2-story Craftsman home boasts an abundance of architectural intricacies. Coffered ceilings in living & dining area. Plantation shutters. Wood floors throughout main level continuing upstairs to the spacious mezzanine. 4 sets of French doors w/enclosed blinds. Kitchen w/granite counters & ceramic tile flr. Updated bathrooms, lower w/step in shower. Back yard designed by master gardener, large deck. Dt garage off alley. Double lot. Tankless water heater. Near downtown, Trader Joes, Kulshan Brewery, parks, trails & schools.

In the heart of enviable Edgemoor, meticulously renovated Mid-Century Modern offers intimate Bay and Island Views. Situated on a private 2/3 acre with clean landscaping + expansive fenced backyard with raised beds and fruit trees. Light-filled interiors with walls of architectural windows and doors. Exceptional finishes from the inside out. Entertaining kitchen with Walnut cabinets, Dacor appliances, granite countertops + spacious island. Large butlers pantry. West-facing Teak deck spanning the length of home. Main floor luxury primary suite. Zone heating/cooling. Lower level with a separate entrance ideal for MIL. Solar, electric charging stations. Stroll to community beaches. Walk to Historic Fairhaven, Ferry/Train Terminal and Dog Park.

This delightful property offers a spacious 2-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom layout with an office. Enjoy the open floorplan, utility room with a deep sink, and front/back decks for outdoor relaxation. A storage shed adds convenience, and all appliances are included. This residence is clean, well-maintained, and move-in ready, offering a hassle-free transition. Experience a sense of community in this neighborhood, with a private feel that allows for peace and tranquility. Residents have access to a clubhouse for gatherings, social events, as well as RV parking if needed. 1 car attached garage with storage, don't miss out on this opportunity to join a vibrant community in one of South Bellingham's most desirable locations! 55+ Community.

Tucked into Sudden Valley's premier Gate 2, this 2250 sq ft 4 bedroom home offers partial lake views from much of the home, including the kitchen. With a flat front yard, new roof, & fresh exterior paint, it exudes curb appeal. The main floor is highlighted by a sunken living room & a floor to ceiling fireplace oozing a groovy, chill vibe. Inside, discover newer flooring & appliances, along w/a tankless HWT. Then step outside onto your massive deck to soak in the scenery. The finished basement boasts potential for an apartment, MIL suite, or office. Enjoy all Sudden Valley amenities & proximity to Lake Whatcom. Sudden Valley amenities include a stunning 18-hole golf course on the shores of Lake Whatcom, marina, beaches, pool, & more.

Discover coastal living at its finest in this stunning 3 bedroom, 2.25 bath home. Built in 2019, this home offers a perfect blend of elegance and functionality and a well-utilized layout that maximizes every bit of its 1610 sqft. Entertain with ease in the expansive gourmet kitchen, featuring exquisite quartz countertops throughout, a unique backsplash, and a convenient walk-in pantry. Relax and unwind in the spacious primary suite, complete with a generous walk-in closet. Situated on a sunny, fully landscaped lot at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, this home offers tranquility and privacy all with A/C. Ample parking for a boat or RV. With its proximity to the beach and a wealth of amenities nearby, this is coastal living at its finest.

Welcome home to this completely renovated gem in the highly sought after Village at Cordata 55+ community. This bright and tastefully updated home has it all; fresh paint, LVP flooring throughout, quartz countertops, all new appliances, dual sink primary bathroom, a newer furnace with A/C, and a newer hot water tank. Enjoy the privacy of this end unit on your quiet patio with mature landscaping. Plenty of room for all your toys and hobbies with a full sized 2 car garage and RV parking! The community amenities are also some of the best offered with an indoor pool and jacuzzi, a wood working center, billiard room, clubhouse with kitchen, and exercise room.

Welcome to this delightful Farmhouse. The spacious living room boasts large windows, a fireplace w/ floor-to-ceiling shiplap detail, & vaulted ceilings. The kitchen is equipped w/ an island, offering extra counter space for preparing delicious meals. Adjacent to the kitchen is a dining room that leads out to a covered deck. The primary bedroom has a south-facing view, ensuite w/ a free-standing bathtub and tile shower, & a large walk-in closet. 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms. This house provides ample room for comfortable living. Two-car garage with workshop space situated on a premium greenbelt lot facing south w/ natural sun & a distant water view. Church Hill Ranch - Model - Farmstead Home will be completed in Early March - Move in Ready

This is truly one-of-a-kind...at nearly 2, 800 sq ft, you'll love this open concept home w/ garage parking for 5 vehicles located in city limits! Boasting 9' + vaulted ceilings, a grand chef's kitchen with granite counters, massive island & S/S appliances, the main level is ideal for entertaining w/ a wide open great room/kitchen/dining space that leads to directly to the backyard covered area. The generously sized primary suite features a private balcony, fireplace, huge walk in closet & ensuite bath. So many options on this 14K+ sq ft lot: RV parking w/ 50amp plug & insulated 25'x20' shop w/ 100 amp power. Conveniently located walking distance to the schools, bustling downtown Blaine, 2 US/CAN borders, a saltwater marina & I-5 access.

Discover this beautifully remodeled Glenhaven home with an extra buildable lot! The great floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the kitchen and dining room, and includes a spacious second family room. Enjoy recent renovations with new flooring throughout. The big master bedroom features a completely remodeled bathroom with a custom walk-in tile shower, and the main bathroom has been updated with tile and a new vanity. Step outside to the expansive, fenced backyard, which offers the potential for division into another lot for future development. Relax in the new gazebo on the paver patio by the fire pit. This home also includes a new roof and a 90% efficient heat pump with AC. Don't miss this incredible opportunity!

Located on a corner lot in the heart of Bellinghams Lettered Streets close to Schools, parks, and a short stroll or ride to thriving downtown & Bellingham's many shops, cafes, Breweries, etc. 4 bedrooms, open floor plan, nice condition, location & bus line access make it suitable to continue as a solid rental or ideal owner occupied home. 2 bedrooms and full bath on main level and 2 bedrooms and bathroom upstairs rooms are good size. Main floor living with kitchen open to dining and living room and nice size pantry. Ample off street driveway parking as well as on street parking. Small garden shed out back. Fully applianced including W&D. Great opportunity to get a home in good shape in very desirable Bellingham location.

Introducing Marigold #41, a charming studio condo boasting abundant natural light and thoughtful furnishings, making it the perfect sanctuary for a cozy retreat. Fully equipped with all your kitchen essentials, this end unit invites you to indulge in effortless living. Experience the best of Sudden Valley living with a myriad of amenities at your fingertips. From kayaking on the waters of Lake Louise to refreshing dips in one of the two pools. Explore the nearby shopping center, perfect your swing on the golf course, or unwind with a scenic stroll along the lakeside trails. Short term rentals allowed. 30 day minimum.

Welcome to your new home! This charming 3-bed, 1.75-bath house offers 1110 sq ft of comfort and convenience. Enjoy ample natural light, a nice eat-in kitchen, fireplace, front porch and cozy bedrooms. Relax on the expansive deck or in the inviting living area. Features a 2-car garage. Perfectly located near amenities. Schedule a viewing today!

Captivating views of Lummi Bay and Rosario Straight from the front windows and a lush Sandy Point Golf course out back. This charming 3/1.75 home, has a spacious primary with Lummi Bay & Rosario Straight views an ensuite bath with a walk-in closet. The kitchen is open to the main living area and is nicely appointed for any home cook. The other two bedrooms each have views, one to the bay and one to the green. Enjoy Sandy Point amenities such as swimming, tennis, a clubhouse, golf and a marina. You must come experience this home in-person. Once you see it you won't want to leave. Live a beautiful easy and fun life everyday.

This Birch Bay Village home on over 1/3 acre corner lot, with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2, 236 square feet and custom designed on one level is looking for someone to put the finishing touches on. Canadian owner has been lovingly working on this home since 1983 and due to health reasons has not been able to completely finish it. Needs flooring and kitchen finished, plus a few other projects to make this home just how you would like it. Out of the flood plain and has wonderful sun exposure. Come take a look at this home and make it yours. Birch Bay Village has 24 hour manned gated security, 9 hole golf course, private marina, clubhouse, 2 man made lakes, saltwater parks and beaches, pickle ball & tennis courts and private quiet roads.

Privacy, nature, and peaceful living converge in this stunning contemporary Silver Beach home! Situated on a sprawling 3 acre lot, this residence offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Located just minutes from downtown and Barkley Village, you can enjoy the best of both worlds, allowing you to retreat into the tranquility of nature while still being within easy reach of urban amenities. The spacious 4- bedroom home features a main floor primary w/ walk-in closet and ensuite bath. Upstairs there are 3+ bedrooms, an office, bonus room, and a storage room. There is plenty of parking with the attached garage + shop. Embrace the opportunity to live, work, and play in a space that offers the freedom to create your own oasis!

Pacific Northwest paradise! Idyllic country living surrounded by scenic mountains and hills, this is the rare, nearly new home you've been dreaming of. A truly spacious retreat & almost 5 acres built with your comfort in mind. Oversized windows showcase exceptional views from each angle of the open concept living/dining/kitchen- even the pantry. Primary design includes oversized tub and massive spa like private bathroom, custom walk in closet and a flex space that could be a second office, workout studio or nursery. A daily Easter egg hunt awaits as the free range chickens lay eggs in the forest! 100 baby trees recently planted on the property. Heat pump, wired for generator, plenty of room for RV parking!

Picture yourself waking up to the soft glow of sunlight filtering through the curtains, casting a warm hue on the original fir floors of your charming craftsman home. As you make your way to the modern, spacious kitchen, the aroma of freshly brewed coffee fills the air. Stepping outside, the serene side yard welcomes you with its lush greenery and vibrant blooms, a testament to the care of a skilled gardener, offering a peaceful retreat in the heart of the Cornwall Park neighborhood. From this prime location, stroll to nearby cafes, breweries, & parks, immersing yourself in the vibrant community that defines Bellingham living. Welcome home to 2814 Russell St, where timeless charm and modern comfort unite for a life of joy & fulfillment.

Welcome to this beautifully upgraded home in the heart of Birch Bay ! Too many upgrades to list ! Right around the corner from the beach. Home has been recently updated with whole new kitchen (including cabinets, slab counter, and SS appliances), flooring, fresh paint, and an expansive deck, perfect for outdoor living. 2 bedrooms / 1 bath. Less than a mile to the town of Birch Bay. Plenty of exterior space to park an RV for your vacationing friends and family who will definitely want to visit ! Welcome to your Birch Bay Beach Getaway!

Extensive updating and remodeling has been done to this 3 bed, 2 bath rambler on a quiet street close to Bham trails, Lake Padden, and Galbraith! This home has been completely transformed and improved, with luxury vinyl plank flooring, recessed lighting, new kitchen and bathrooms with quartz counters, new gas fireplace insert, air conditioning, and more! High-quality, large windows give the home ample natural light, and the open layout and huge kitchen island make for a great entertaining space where dining, kitchen & living room all connect. With a finished 2-car garage and a large shed in the fully fenced backyard, this home offers tons of storage for your outdoor gear. Only minutes to world-class hiking, biking, and lake access!

Wake up in the morning and watch Mt Baker, with its spindrift turning all the colors, reflected on Birch Bay, watch fantastic sunrise after sunrise, while you have your coffee.Hop in your golf cart, down to the marina and grab your kayaks or boat from the private marina, get on the peaceful water and harvest your crab pots, eat delicious crabs with handpicked organic blackberry pies that evening. This unparalleled lifestyle is yours, along with a darling, well maintained one level home with two relaxing decks on a large lot. In rainshadowed Birch Bay, there's more sunny days to enjoy this home. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity. This property offers exceptional value and is a must-see in Birch Bay Village.

Welcome to this charming one-story home in beautiful Birch Bay area. This home features 4 bd/2 bath, a large fully fenced and very private and tranquil backyard that abuts to a lush greenbelt area offering a tranquil setting with nature views. The home features a new roof, fresh exterior paint, new flooring and carpeting throughout, a/c for your comfort, AND new hot water heater. Located just minutes away from the I-5 freeway and Canadian Border, and minutes to Birch Bay beach, offering both convenience and coastal lifestyle. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your new home!
